node.text: Finished Red Tailed Tropicbird sculpture. NFS. I was asked to make a commission with seabirds from Hawaii. I chose these beautiful birds and made a background representing the mountains, the coastal waters and the deep ocean. These birds nest in the cliffs, sometimes far inland and on the steepest inclines and then hunt out at see for squid that come up from the deep ocean. You can see several species of Tropicbirds throughout Hawaii, try the Kilauea lighthouse on Kaua’i to see for them for yourself! #flamework #flameworking #lampwork #lampworking #glass #redtailedtropicbird #tropicbird #bird #headyart #glassofig #highshelfglass #borosilicate #borofauna
